<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <!-- try to get it so that it's nice to view on any device -->
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

        <title>The City of Deshangria</title>

        <!-- import the styles the website will use, and the css stuff -->
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;600;700;900&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="Deshangria_website_style.css">
    </head>
    <body>

        <!-- ========================= BANNER =============================== -->
        <header class="SiteBanner">
            <div class="BannerInner">
                <span class="BannerCrest">⚔️</span>
                <div class="BannerText">
                    <h1 class="BannerTitle">Deshangria</h1>
                    <p class="BannerSub">Capital of the Kingdom of Solitude</p>
                </div>
                <span class="BannerCrest">🏔️</span>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- ========================= NAVIGATION STUFF =============================== -->
        <nav id="navBar">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="Home Page.html" class="active">🏠 Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="dayinthelife.html">☀️ Day in the Life</a></li>
                <li><a href="history.html">📜 History</a></li>
                <li><a href="blacksmith.html">⚒️ Blacksmith</a></li>
                <li><a href="theater.html">🎭 Theater</a></li>
                <li><a href="hunting.html">🐺 Hunting</a></li>
                <li><a href="helpcenter.html">❓ Help Center</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>

        <!-- ========================= MAIN CITY PICTURE =============================== -->
        <section class="CityPicture">
            <div class="CityOverlay"></div>
            <img src="Images/Home page images/City_Picture.png" alt="The City of Deshangria" class="CityIMG">
            <div class="CityCaption">
                <p>The bustling city of Deshangria</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ========================= MAIN CITY PICTURE =============================== -->
        <main>
            <div class="ClassContainer reveal">
                <h2>Welcome to Deshangria</h2>
                <p>
                    Why hello there fellow traveler! Here to see our great city of Deshangria are you? Or maybe you're here
                    to stay 😱??? WELL LUCKY FOR YOU, WE'RE AWESOME🤪!! We, the Deshangria city council created a special
                    guide to help you get aclimated to life around here much faster then you would at any other run down 
                    city. So get excited enjoy the virtual tour of our wonderful city, Deshangria! 
                </p>
                <p>
                    P.S. this website is only viewable for beings who are moving here or sponsered to travel here. With that being said, don't you feel special😁?
                </p>

                <!-- Video Tour -->
                <h2>Virtual Tour of the City Market</h2>
                <p>
                    Come explore Deshangria's awesome market place without even having to go out side! do be warned though
                    after watching this you definitly will want to go out side!
                </p>
                <div class="VideoWrapper">
                    <video controls width="100%">
                        <source src="Images\Home page images\video.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                        Your browser does not support the video tag.  <!-- Incase it does not load-->
                    </video>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ========================= CONTENT PAGE CARDS =============================== -->
            <!-- I always thought these looked cool in other websites so I wanted them and boy did they not disappoint-->
            <div class="ClassContainer reveal">
                <h2>Discover More About Deshangria</h2>
                <p>Click any section below to learn more about Deshangria.</p>

                <div class="CardGrid">
                    <a href="dayinthelife.html" class="PageCard">
                        <span class="CardIcon">☀️</span>
                        <h3>Day in the Life</h3>
                        <p>
                            Scared about what life is like here? Don't be, come see how life is for some of the locals around 
                            the city. Don't worry, this place is very welcoming of new comers!
                        </p>
                        <span class="CardLink">Explore Daily Life</span>
                    </a>

                    <a href="history.html" class="PageCard">
                        <span class="CardIcon">📜</span>
                        <h3>History</h3>
                        <p>
                            From the original 7 civilizations, to the Great Siege, to the current status of life diver deeper
                            into the origins of this beautiful land.
                        </p>
                        <span class="CardLink">Learn the History</span>
                    </a>

                    <a href="blacksmith.html" class="PageCard">
                        <span class="CardIcon">⚒️</span>
                        <h3>Blacksmith</h3>
                        <p>
                            Known for our ground breaking technology, our forges are no different come check out our 
                            renowned blacksmith shop for yourself
                        </p>
                        <span class="CardLink">Visit the Forge</span>
                    </a>

                    <a href="theater.html" class="PageCard">
                        <span class="CardIcon">🎭</span>
                        <h3>Theater</h3>
                        <p>
                            Catch the latest showings at Deshangria's beloved theater. Check the schedule and grab your seat.
                            It's free by the way😁!
                        </p>
                        <span class="CardLink">See What's Playing</span>
                    </a>

                    <a href="hunting.html" class="PageCard">
                        <span class="CardIcon">🐺</span>
                        <h3>Hunting Grounds</h3>
                        <p>
                            Are you a hunter? Lucky for you Deshangria is home to some of the most formidible predators in the land. Check out the beasts you'll be up against!
                        </p>
                        <span class="CardLink">Learn to Hunt</span>
                    </a>

                    <a href="helpcenter.html" class="PageCard">
                        <span class="CardIcon">❓</span>
                        <h3>Help Center</h3>
                        <p>
                            Any questions? No problem! give our help center a message and we'll get back to you as soon as possible
                        </p>
                        <span class="CardLink">Get Help</span>
                    </a>

                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <!-- ========================= FOOTER =============================== -->
        <!-- It will be the same across the board-->
        <footer>
            <p>🏔️ <strong>Deshangria</strong> — Capital of the Kingdom of Solitude</p>
            <p>
                <a href="helpcenter.html">Help Center</a> ·
                <a href="">Contact Us</a> · <!-- Fake Contact Link -->
                <!-- we need external links so I added this random one to some D&D like stuff :) -->
                <a href="https://forgottenrealms.fandom.com/wiki/Forgotten_Realms_Wiki" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kingdom Archives</a>
            </p>
            <p>© Year 1247 of the Third Age · All rights reserved by the Crown of Solitude</p>
        </footer>

        <script src="scroll-reveal.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>
